<p><strong>Product Details</strong></p>
<p>The Custom Jr. is an ultra-slim flatware organizer.  This unit was designed for flatware in narrow drawers.  You decide the width (up to 16&#8243;) and usable depth needed (up to 13&#8243;).  Our Custom Jr. organizers are bottomless, have adjustable dividers, and are custom made.  The Custom Jr. is unique in that it is meant to fill your drawer width, but not necessarily your drawer depth.  We&#8217;ll size the organizer&#8217;s depth based on your longest flatware utensil up to 13&#8243; in length.  You&#8217;ll also get the versatility of a classic, traditional slot-and-divider system.  Movable dividers allow micro-adjustability to make the most of your space.  We make the organizer insert bottomless for easy cleaning. This custom  organizer includes four hardwood wedges to lock it in place &#8212; no more  sliding organizer!</p>

